      "role": "user",
      "content": "ok that makes sense. since i'm dealing with all these roots and the soil stuff, i'm worried about what's happening underneath the surface where i can't see it. is there anything else i should watch out for in the dirt or the root area to make sure the plant stays healthy once it's in the new pot?",
